title: New: Elena – I Don't Know Where You've Been Before
body:
Having taken the past week or so off from writing, it’s rather refreshing to come back to something like this beauty from Auckland’s **Elena**.

_I Don’t Know Where You’ve Been Before_ pretty much summarises one of the first thoughts that goes through anyone’s mind when embarking upon a new relationship; the concern about the past and the anticipation for the future, and it’s never sounded so gorgeous. Check it out below.
